A_056 - As for the &ldquo;problem&rdquo; of flatulence, it must be said that being something totally involuntary and difficult to control, any judgment on the matter, conceptually speaking, is completely meaningless and groundless. In any case, for those who need it, there is a technique to do them silently: you have to misalign your legs by putting one further forward and one further back (when sitting) and with a little attention you can do it.